desc: Seriously Keto Singapore is your one stop shop for  keto and low carb treats and products. Our keto bakery specializes in delicious low carb bread, cakes, desserts, snacks and beverages.

layout.text:
When we thought of flavors that could truly be a treat for the special men in our lives, we knew that we hit the jackpot with chocolate and peanut butter!

Treat daddy dearest this Father's Day with our limited edition Chocolate Peanut Butter Cake. Available in single slices and 20cm Whole Cake. 

Celebrate without worry and indulge without the guilt! Our suited up cake for HIM is low-carb, keto-compliant and diabetic friendly AND, with island-wide delivery, we'll send these bad boys straight to your doorstep!
Available from now till June 19.
